<NEW>

There was a slow nod from SKYSHADOW and then he looked up at HYDRAS,
being that the Predacon commander was larger than he. "Sir, I was only
communicating with my Fuzors."

He turned to look at the MAXIMALS, but his words were still low and
directed only at HYDRAS, "We are about to enter the jungle and
communications are about to be cut off. I wanted to set up last orders
before that happened."
